svg.text: help investor pecunia beat the moneytaur

Mythonancial is a web game created to help college students and anyone else to learn more about invest-ments.This game won 2nd place for Finra’s Money Management Hack at Techni-ca 2018, the world’s largest All-Wom-en and Non-Binary hackathon. All elements of the game was developed under 24 hours.HTML, CSS, JS, Phaser.JS, Adobe Illustrator
I was in charge of creating all graphics as well as coding the game.
